branchCategory.name: CDQ2*P, Compact Cylinder, High Magnetic Field Design
branchCategory.description: For welding environments, this standard double acting, single rod version of the CQ2 compact cylinder includes a high magnetic field capable magnet and a rod coil scraper. The CQ2 is available in bore sizes from 50mm to 80mm. It comes standard with male or female piston rod threads. It is possible to mount auto switches on any of the 4 surfaces.
